Makes about 1/4 cup

    1 small can of unseasoned tomato paste, ~6oz
    3 Tbs worcestershire sauce
    3 Tbs ketchup
    2 Tbs molasses (not blackstrap)
    1 tsp garlic powder
    1/8 tsp salt, to taste
    
Combine ingredients in a small pot and bring to a simmer. Simmer about 10 mins, stirring occasionally.

It keeps in the fridge for up to 1 week.

